				<p><a href="#" class="btn-small">Read more</a></p>
	</div>


<div class="grid_5 omega">
				<h2>Get Bakin' with Us</h2>

			<div id="Contact">
				<div class="phone">
				    1-555-cup-cake<br>
				
					<p>Email us:<a href="#">bakecon@smellslikebakin.com</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p>We announce all our new flavours first through Facebook &amp; Twitter, and even take request</p>

